{"tid":925654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"普通市民冇責任幫任何人/政府表達你想聽既意見","createTime":"2018-12-03T01:47:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T01:47:10.000Z","uid":175623,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b736701e11591384dba029192ae5e67383ca5b82","tid":925654,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T01:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bWJutBd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbWJutBd.png&h=3f2fc769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我把口係我既，我鍾意出就就出聲，收聲就收聲，我唔出聲唔代表我支持定反對，我唔反對你地做既野唔代表我支持佢。最簡單既邏輯推論都做唔到，你唔好玩政治啦，比外國人笑你傻撚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再舉一個例子，我係唔係一定要出聲反對強姦先？唔會聲會唔會犯法？唔答你問題會唔會犯法？如果唔會，咁我唔出聲有咩問題？你屈我支持就係你唔岩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}